d earn income  In addition to two five week regular summer terms  the Summer Session also administers the Summer Study Abroad Program  the Summer Undergraduate Research Institute and the Summer Transition Program  Register for Summer Courses   Catalogue Summer Session Course Lists Tuition   Fees Important Dates  Canceled Courses Courses Subject to Cancellation Attendance   Refund Policies  Summer Forms Barracks Check In Staff Academics Home Summer Programs at VMI Summer Session Summer Transition Program Undergraduate Research  SURI  Teresa Evans Administrative Assistant 303 Shell Hall Virginia Military Institute Lexington  VA  24450 P   540  464 7213 F   540  464 7726 E evanstl vmi edu  Academics Home Summer Programs at VMI Summer Session Summer Transition Program Undergraduate Research  SURI  Teresa Evans Administrative Assistant 303 Shell Hall Virginia Military Institute Lexington  VA  24450 P   540  464 7213 F   540  464 7726 E evanstl vmi edu Academics Home Summer Programs at VMI Summer Session Summer Transition Program Undergraduate Research  SURI Academics Home Academics Home Summer Programs at VMI Summer Programs at VMI Summer Session Summer Session Summer Session Summer Transition Program Summer Transition Program Undergraduate Research  SURI Undergraduate Research  SURI Teresa Evans Administrative Assistant 303 Shell Hall Virginia Military Institute Lexington  VA  24450 P   540  464 7213 F   540  464 7726 E evanstl vmi edu Teresa Evans Administrative Assistant 303 Shell Hall Virginia Military Institute Lexington  VA  24450 P   540  464 7213 F   540  464 7726 E evanstl vmi edu Teresa Evans Administrative Assistant  303 Shell Hall Virginia Military Institute Lexington  VA  24450   P   540  464 7213 F   540  464 7726 E evanstl vmi edu   evanstl vmi edu Home   Academics   Programs   Summer Programs   Summer Session 2016 Summer Session VMI Summer Session is available to facilitate a cadets  progression toward degree completion by offering courses for academic cr